Package: RAIPlot
Title: AI-Powered Adaptive Plot Generator for RStudio
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your Name", "Your Email", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An RStudio Addin that uses AI (OpenAI GPT) to generate adaptive 
    ggplot2 visualizations based on user descriptions and data characteristics.
    The tool intelligently parses your data, understands your plotting requirements,
    and automatically generates publication-ready plots.
